== Welcome to LiFiDeA

LiFiDeA is a platform for managing personal information.

It has several key benefits:

* You can collect your information of any format from arbitrary sources in your desktop as well as on the web
* You can access your information by combining keyword search, associative browsing and faceted search
* Your information is organized automatically while you use the system

For more information on the design of LiFiDeA, visit wiki : https://github.com/jykim/lifidea/wiki

